---
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Heritage Coastal | Respectful Property Transitions</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Private acquisition of coastal homes, estates, and legacy properties. Respectful conversations, flexible timing, and thoughtful transitions."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <style is:inline>
      :root {
        --navy: #13243a;
        --navy-2: #1d3048;
        --cream: #f7f2e8;
        --paper: #fbf8f1;
        --linen: #ebe2d3;
        --gold: #c8ad73;
        --gold-dark: #a88747;
        --ink: #182638;
        --muted: #68706a;
        --line: rgba(24, 38, 56, 0.14);
        --shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(19, 36, 58, 0.16);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--paper);
        color: var(--ink);
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .site-header {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        z-index: 5;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 34px 0;
        color: white;
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .monogram {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(200, 173, 115, 0.72);
        color: var(--gold);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .brand-name {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.24em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .header-note {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 760px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        color: white;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 82% 18%, rgba(200, 173, 115, 0.18), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(19, 36, 58, 0.98), rgba(19, 36, 58, 0.94) 52%, rgba(29, 48, 72, 0.9));
      }

      .hero::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background:
          linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(19, 36, 58, 0.96), rgba(19, 36, 58, 0.72) 58%, rgba(19, 36, 58, 0.48)),
          url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2400&q=85");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        opacity: 0.42;
        filter: saturate(0.82) contrast(0.95);
      }

      .hero-inner {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 190px 0 150px;
      }

      .eyebrow,
      .section-label,
      .step-label,
      .num {
        color: var(--gold);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.22em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 920px;
        margin: 24px 0 28px;
        font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 88px);
        line-height: 0.96;
        letter-spacing: -0.055em;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        font-size: clamp(19px, 2vw, 23px);
        line-height: 1.68;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 38px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 52px;
        padding: 15px 26px;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 0.035em;
        transition: transform 160ms ease, background 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .button-primary {
        background: var(--gold);
        color: var(--navy);
      }

      .button-secondary {
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.38);
        color: white;
      }

      .commitments {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 3;
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: -72px auto 0;
        background: var(--paper);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        border: 1px solid rgba(200, 173, 115, 0.28);
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      .commitment {
        padding: 34px 36px;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .commitment:last-child {
        border-right: 0;
      }

      .commitment strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: var(--navy);
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .commitment span {
        display: block;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 112px 0;
      }

      .section-inner {
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .split {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.92fr 1.08fr;
        gap: clamp(46px, 8vw, 110px);
        align-items: start;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        color: var(--navy);
        font-size: clamp(36px, 4.6vw, 60px);
        line-height: 1.06;
        letter-spacing: -0.042em;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .body-copy p {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.78;
      }

      .linen {
        background: var(--linen);
      }

      .section-heading {
        max-width: 780px;
      }

      .cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 26px;
        margin-top: 54px;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--paper);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 40px 36px;
        min-height: 286px;
      }

      .num {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        font-size: 11px;
      }

      h3 {
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        color: var(--navy);
        font-size: 29px;
        line-height: 1.16;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.72;
      }

      .process-list {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .process-step {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 145px 1fr;
        gap: 30px;
        padding: 34px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }

      .process-step p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 19px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .statement {
        background: var(--navy);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 112px 24px;
      }

      .statement p {
        max-width: 1040px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-size: clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 56px);
        line-height: 1.22;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .contact-card {
        background: var(--linen);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 46px;
      }

      .contact-card p {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.72;
      }

      .email-link {
        color: var(--navy);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
      }

      .site-footer {
        background: var(--navy);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66);
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer-inner {
        width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 32px 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .site-header {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 16px;
        }

        .hero {
          min-height: auto;
        }

        .hero-inner {
          padding: 170px 0 116px;
        }

        .commitments,
        .split,
        .cards,
        .process-step {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .commitment {
          border-right: 0;
          border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        }

        .commitment:last-child {
          border-bottom: 0;
        }

        .section {
          padding: 82px 0;
        }

        .footer-inner {
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 560px) {
        .brand-name {
          letter-spacing: 0.17em;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 46px;
        }

        .hero-actions {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .button {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Heritage Coastal home">
        <span class="monogram">H</span>
        <span class="brand-name">Heritage Coastal</span>
      </a>
      <div class="header-note">Private property transitions</div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-inner">
          <div class="eyebrow">Stewardship · Continuity · Respect</div>
          <h1>A thoughtful path for owners considering the future of a cherished property.</h1>
          <p class="hero-copy">
            Heritage Coastal works directly with homeowners, families, and estates seeking a private, respectful, and dignified transition of coastal real estate.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="mailto:info@heritagecoastal.com">Start a Private Conversation</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="#approach">Our Approach</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="commitments" aria-label="Heritage Coastal commitments">
        <div class="commitment">
          <strong>Private</strong>
          <span>Quiet conversations without public listings, open houses, or neighborhood speculation.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment">
          <strong>Patient</strong>
          <span>Flexible timing for families, estates, and owners who need room to decide carefully.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment">
          <strong>Direct</strong>
          <span>Clear proposals, straightforward terms, and conversations with decision-makers.</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="approach">
        <div class="section-inner split">
          <div>
            <div class="section-label">Our Philosophy</div>
            <h2>Properties deserve more than a transaction.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="body-copy">
            <p>
              Many homes represent decades of care, family history, and personal investment. Decisions involving those properties deserve patience and respect.
            </p>
            <p>
              We provide a direct path for owners who may be ready to sell, but do not want pressure, public exposure, repeated showings, or unnecessary complexity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section linen">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <div class="section-label">Why Owners Work With Us</div>
            <h2>Quiet, direct, and considerate.</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="cards">
            <article class="card">
              <span class="num">01</span>
              <h3>Respect for the owner</h3>
              <p>
                We move at a pace that suits the family, not the market. No hard sell. No manufactured urgency. No public pressure.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
              <span class="num">02</span>
              <h3>Respect for the property</h3>
              <p>
                Every property has a story. We take time to understand its history, condition, setting, and the owner’s hopes for what comes next.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="card">
              <span class="num">03</span>
              <h3>Respect for privacy</h3>
              <p>
                Conversations remain private. Options can be discussed quietly, without listing, staging, repeated showings, or speculation.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-inner split">
          <div>
            <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
            <h2>A simpler alternative to a public sale.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="process-list">
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-label">First</div>
              <p>We have a private conversation to understand the property, the timing, and whether a direct transaction may be appropriate.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-label">Second</div>
              <p>If there is mutual interest, we review the property carefully and provide a clear proposal without requiring repairs, staging, or open houses.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-label">Third</div>
              <p>The owner chooses the path and timing. We can accommodate flexible closing dates, estate situations, family transitions, and as-is sales.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="statement">
        <p>We believe the best property transitions are built on trust, clarity, and mutual respect.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-inner split">
          <div>
            <div class="section-label">Contact</div>
            <h2>Begin with a private conversation.</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card">
            <p>
              Whether you are considering a sale, managing an estate, or planning for the future of a family property, we welcome a confidential discussion.
            </p>
            <p>
              Email: <a class="email-link" href="mailto:info@heritagecoastal.com">info@heritagecoastal.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div>© 2026 Heritage Coastal</div>
        <div>Private acquisition of coastal homes and legacy properties</div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
